name: The First Encounter
description:
The first encounter talk about the first time neko peeps met someone from outside of their universe, someone? something? they never knew. what they knew is it was the first time they met Heart the loving character who thaught them a lot about love. When was the first time you met heart?

This is my first art collaboration that i made with one 
and only @sjariftan.


I never thought i would be minting an art since me and my family, we don’t have any art skill. But look, someone collected my work, it just made me happy.

If i can do it, i know you too. Do whatever you want to do, Stan Lee once said “If you have an idea that you genuinely think it’s good don’t let some idiot talk you out of it”
